{"tid":2293731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮超低胸晚裝大露事業線　佘詩曼留言讚「超靚」","createTime":"2020-11-20T12:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T06:31:38.000Z","uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d688e19cc7078bf0140134e5468765b970916706","tid":2293731,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-58-13Ea44dQnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-58-13Ea44dQnn.jpg&h=f474f72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超蓮近日出席電影活動，久未公開露面的她悉心打扮，穿上低胸黑色晚裝，白皙膚色加上豐滿上圍，盡展凹凸有致曼妙身材，而且貴為賭王千金，超蓮本來就自帶一份貴氣，簡約俐落造型既性感又高貴，就連演員佘詩曼也不禁留言大讚「超靚」！<br />\n<br />\n超蓮為穿上這件緊身晚裝，努力運動保持身材，更笑指「成果不錯吧」。除了分享靚相，超蓮亦不忘呼籲粉絲收看由內地演員男友竇驍擔正的新劇《燕雲台》，雖然劇中竇驍飾演唐嫣青梅竹馬的戀人，但超蓮一點也不呷醋，更為男友落力宣傳，認真大方！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-58-34mQYdWci3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-58-34mQYdWci3.jpg&h=33433ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-58-34lvu0sXkR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-58-34lvu0sXkR.jpg&h=a049aa6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-58-34zQo4ceuE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-58-34zQo4ceuE.jpg&h=c2a1a4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-59-02TxAPPcnH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-59-02TxAPPcnH.jpg&h=78063385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/2020-11-19-16-58-34mqpVNJDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F2020-11-19-16-58-34mqpVNJDg.jpg&h=f6ffe619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=413489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D413489&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=0f43e4dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fentertainment%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D413489&h=86c146bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/entertainment/player?newsId=413489</a>"},{"pid":"b9062617433edec83dca23680254768099476704","tid":2293731,"uid":71632,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:44:02.000Z","msg":"A cup比盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc539daed8cace27efe09771299a16f35a951cb2","tid":2293731,"uid":314983,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c02ef52abbc0a79dfb1909012123271d2f1a0d","tid":2293731,"uid":77717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bc539daed8cace27efe09771299a16f35a951cb2","tid":2293731,"uid":314983,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:45:41.000Z","msg":"like china chicken"},{"pid":"ee87f3d7459b286b9ffa28a2076092adff82cf5a","tid":2293731,"uid":30503,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"咁有錢,對奶應該好滑"},{"pid":"7b20730f10c559f29a6235ddcccf5ed588f1874b","tid":2293731,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"對奶縮左水<img sr